title: Les Aliments O Sole Mio, Inc., Recalls Poultry Products Produced without Benefit of Inspection
summary: WASHINGTON, Oct. 31, 2018 Les Aliments O Sole Mio, Inc., a Boisbriand, Quebec, Canada establishment, is recalling approximately 3,880 pounds of chicken tortellini products that were produced without the benefit of inspection by the Canadian Food Inspection Agency (CFIA) and imported into the United States...
